[I] Multiple Arcade Machine Emulator

[T] Xmame is a port of the Multiple Arcade Machine Emulator (MAME) for UNIX
[T] and other POSIX operating systems, which emulates classic arcade games.

[U] https://mame.net

[A] Mame team
[M] Leonel Iván Saafigueroa <leonel@saafigueroa.com.ar>

[C] extra/emulator

[L] GPL
[V] 0.288

[CV-TR] s/\.//
[D] cff5dd98c528bfe8c5da249a876e171d671a4715893cd8a7f3ab81e6 mame0288.tar.gz https://github.com/mamedev/mame/archive/

var_append makeopt ' ' "MY_CPU=`echo $arch | arch2uname | sed s/x86_64/amd64/`"
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_INSERT ' ' "`pkg-config x11 --cflags --libs-only-L`"
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -c?:-lSDL2
makeinstopt=
hook_add postmake 5 "install mame $root$bindir/"
